### ğŸ“Œ Commonly Used Tags

* <b> â†’ Bold text
* <i> â†’ Italic text
* <em> â†’ Emphasized text (similar to italic, but more meaningful)
* <strong> â†’ Strong importance (similar to bold, but more meaningful)
* <small> â†’ Smaller text
* <br> â†’ Line break



